# apps/unlock/pkg/catalog/catalog.yaml
#
# Canonical unlock SITE CATALOG — the foundation for aligning our site library,
# rule sets and detection to the MediaUnlockTest reference (unlock.icmp.ing).
#
# WHAT THIS IS: data only. Each entry names a service, its region bucket(s), the
# MediaUnlockTest provider function that detects it (bound in P1), and a best-effort
# routing rule source for mihomo (P3). It does NOT vendor any detection code and is
# NOT wired into config generation yet — it is consumed deliberately by later phases.
#
# routingStatus:
#   geosite  - mapped to a Loyalsoldier/v2ray-rules-dat geosite category, VERIFIED to
#              exist in v2fly/domain-list-community (1504-category index). High confidence.
#   domains  - no geosite category exists; seeded with the service's own identifying
#              domain (shared CDN/platform hosts rejected). P3 should confirm/expand.
#   none     - no clean routing source available (game endpoints / shared infra only).
#              P3 must research proper rules. Detection still works regardless.
#
# Generated deterministically from MediaUnlockTest v1.9.2-1782574315 lists.go. Provenance &
# regeneration: see README.md. Geosite categories validated against the same upstream
# the panel rule-mirror serves (Loyalsoldier/v2ray-rules-dat).

